before considering the non-mandatory source listed in paragraph
(b). See 7.105(b) and part 19 regarding consideration of small
businesses and socioeconomic programs.</p>
                     <p>(a)</p>
                     <p>(1) <b>Supplies</b>. FSS, Governmentwide acquisition
contracts, multi-agency contracts, and other procurement
instruments intended for use by multiple agencies, including BPAs
under FSS contracts (e.g., FSSI BPAs).</p>
                     <p>(2) <b>Services</b>. Agencies are encouraged to
consider Federal Prison Industries, Inc., as well as the sources
listed in paragraph (a)(1) of this section.</p>
                     <p>(b) <b>Commercial open market sources</b> (to include
commercial platforms).</p>
